Talk to the Cook's Guild Leader in Minas Morgul
'These pies produce the most enticing aroma in the oven, would you not agree?'
The crafting recipes you must create can be found in your crafting panel.\n\nBake up fifteen servings of Nine Star Pie.

'What could be better than a Seven-star Stew? A pie filled with Seven-star Stew, that's what! Add in tangy goat's cheese from the dwarves and some sweet cherry sauce from Rohan and you have a truly special meal. You will want to master this recipe.'
